There was so much I wanted to write, but instead I’ll just say; Designing, directing and creating for women & anyone who identifies as one WITH SUCH A BAD ASS TEAM OF WOMEN is the coolest DayDream & I’ll never ever take it for granted. Cheers to the new year. Xx  #fredericksofhollywood

Congratulations to beautiful, ethereal @kaliuchis 
Humbled to be able to drape you in this gown during such a powerful and beautiful moment. This entire piece was a collaboration of women. 

Created with beautiful @jesuisjeniece. Your aura is as powerful and as beautiful as the stones you create art with. Belly on the gown fully adorned with Jeniece’s stones. Thank you for your art ✨

Thank you @lucamarieg @umanataliag for bringing me into your vision/styling during this moment. 

Women are the most magical beings to me. This was more than a collaboration of creativity and I’m still in awe of what we all did. 

It was so important this felt effortless so I draped the entire gown. Cutting each tier and flounce to drape and fit perfect in proportion to everything. 

Watch @kaliuchis new video now to witness the beauty of it all 🤍

The dress for @kaliuchis Tu Corazon Es Mio/Diosa music video with @jesuisjeniece goddess jewel and stone strands across the belly
styled by @lucamarieg & @umanataliag 

I wish you could see the stitched silk chiffon godets in and down the front that waterfall to and throughout the hem.
